  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS muhsu\nDeews dewe arridsan Ogu to\nKehnixu no Bahsana muhsu\nRohkâ/lihds ar wiſſeein winna\nLaudim/ un mehs kawain to/ ka-\nmeir winnam neneeka atlifke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un mehs usachman tanni\nLaikâ wiſſus winna Pilsfahtus/\nne weens Pilsfahts bija/ ko mehs\nne buhtum no winna nehmuschi/\nfefchdefmits Pilsfahti / wiſſu\nGarrumu no Argob/ to Walsti-\nbu Og Bahsand.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi tee Pilsfahti bija ar\naugsteem Muhreem/ Wahrtim\nun Klinkeem stiprinati/ bes wehl\ndauds zittahm Meestahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un mehs isdeldejam tohs/\nittin ka mehs Stoam tam Keh-\nnixam no Esbona bijam darriſ-\nfchi/ isdeldedami wiſſos Pilsfah-\ntos Wihrus/ Seewas un Behr-\nnixus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet wiſſus Lohpus/ un to\nPilsfahtn Laupijumii rehmam\nmehs preeſch muns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta jehman mehs tanni\nLaikâ to Semini/ no to diweju\nAmoriteru Kehnixu Rohkas/\nwinnapus Jardanas/ no Arno-\nna Uppes lihds Ernona Kalnam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "(Tee Zihdonitert nosauz to\nErmonu Sirion/ bet tee Amori-\nteri fanz winnu Seentr.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſus Pilsfahtus Klaj-\njunâ/ un to wiſſu Gileadu un\nwiſſu Bahsanu lihds Salkai un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Ogs tas Kehnixsch n\nBahsana bija ween atlizzis n\nteem atliffuscheem Milseem/red\nwixxa Gulta/ weena dselsu Gul\nta / neggi ta irr Rabbatâ t\nBehrnu Ammon/ dewia Ohlekt\nirr winnas Garrums/ un tfchets\nOhlefts winnas Plattums/ peh\nweena Wihra Elkou.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu to paschu Sem\nmi eemantojam mehs tanni Lai\nkâ/ no Aroera/ kas pee Arnona\nuppes irr/ un weenn Pufti n\nGileadas Kalna ar taweem Pils\nfahtcem dewu es teem Ruhbent\ntereem un Gaditereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas atlizzis bija no Gi-\nleadas/ un wiſſu Bahsanu / te\nWalstitbu Oga dewu es Mana-\nfus puss Zilti/ wiſſu Walstu Ar-\ngob zaur wiſſu Bahsanu: Sch-\npatti tappe faukta to Milsu Lau-\nschu Semme.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jairs ManaffiusDehis dab-\nbuja wiſſu ArgobaWalstu/ lihd\nto Geſturiteru un Madkatiteru\nRobbeschai / un wiſsch nosauze\nto pehz fawu Wahrdru: Bahsan-\nAwot-Jäiru/ lihds fchai Deenat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Makiram dewu es Gi-\nleadu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet teem Ruhbenitereem\nun Gaditereem dewu es no Gile-\nadas lihds Arnona Uppei weenu\nPuſſitahs Gelejas un tahs Rob-\nbeschais/ un lihds tai Jaboka Up-\npei/ Amona Behrnu Robbeschai,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Klajunuu / un te\n"
    }
  ],
